NovaPay — local setup (plain text; extend this file instead of adding new .md)

PostgreSQL (primary + read replicas):
  From repo root: cd infra/postgres
  From nova-pay:   cd ../infra/postgres
  cp .env.example .env && docker compose up -d

App env:
  Copy nova-pay/.env.example to .env when you add one; set DATABASE_WRITE_URL and
  DATABASE_READ_URL to match Docker ports (see infra/postgres README).

Run API:
  cd nova-pay && yarn install && yarn start:dev

Swagger:
  http://localhost:3000/api (default PORT=3000)

Architecture rules for agents:
  .cursor/rules/nova-architecture.md
  .cursor/rules/global.md
